  "title": "Process Engineer #75664",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Waste Management</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Process Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Tuas (Company transport provided)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon - Fri, 8.00am - 5.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary up to $4,300 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Analyze and evaluate current processes, take measurements, and interpret data, including SCADA system operations</li><li>Conduct risk assessments to ensure safe operations</li><li>Research, design, and develop processes to improve productivity and workflow</li><li>Oversee day-to-day operations and maintenance of facility processes</li><li>Organize and set up efficient operations</li><li>Manage the implementation of new processes and procedures</li><li>Troubleshoot and resolve issues related to processes, procedures, and operations</li><li>Develop best practices, routines, and innovative solutions to improve output and quality</li><li>Manage process costs and timelines</li><li>Prepare process documentation and operating instructions</li><li>Participate in Process Safety Management (PSM) and Hazard and Operability (Hazop) studies</li><li>Plan and execute plant shutdowns as a turn-key manager</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in Chemical Engineering</li><li>At least 2 years of experience in the process industry</li><li>Good knowledge of process standards, process improvement, and safety management</li><li>Team-oriented and adaptable</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#75664 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
